pageContext.claim: “That's almost a couple of hundred more ships. So you're going to be around for a long time. We're not running out of equipment. We're not running out of ships. And that's been approved, and we are honored by it.”
pageContext.analysis: Going from 283 ships to 355 is not "a couple hundred more ships." Moreover, the funding has not been approved. The ships have not been authorized yet and Congress has to appropriate the necessary funds every year.
